<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="train-v">train <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /treɪn/    美 /treɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(受) 训练；(受) 培训：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sports help to train a person’s character. 
运动有助于培养人的性格。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The school basketball team is <strong>training</strong> hard <strong>for</strong> the league match. 
校篮球队正在刻苦训练备战联赛。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>trainer /'treɪnə(r)/ n [C]   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I always wanted to do the job which I’d been trained <strong><em>_</em></strong>_.   （2011 浙江改）<br />
C.by<br />
D.of  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>